      <title>印尼称 2025 年预算赤字可能低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/indonesia-says-2025-budget-deficit-may-be-smaller-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼立法者同意扩大明年预算赤字的目标范围，赤字可能会比之前估计的要小。]]></description>
